snippet.title: Tour de France 2020 - Time Trial Gameplay | PS4
snippet.description:
Discover the new time-trial gameplay of Tour de France 2020 !

Now you'll have to adapt and manage your TT position but also your effort to regain your energy. 
Tour de France 2020 releases June 4th on PlayStation 4.
